---
title: Sweet-Soy Eggplant, Chicken & Cucumber Slaw Bowl with Sesame Dressing & Crispy Shallots
description: Eggplant roasted in the oven has to be one of our favourite veggies. The sweet and soy seasoning gives it a special
boost of flavour and the refreshing cucumber slaw drizzled over with sesame dressing tastes divine.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
